Enum Mode backed by u8 has idle be 0; active be 1.

Record Point has x: i32; y: i32.

To point for mode mode: Mode, giving Point.
Give match mode:
Mode.idle gives Point with x be 0 and y be 0;
Mode.active gives Point with x be 3 and y be 4;
otherwise gives Point with x be 1 and y be 1.

To main, giving i32.
Let p be point for mode Mode.active.
Give p.x plus p.y.
